<h2 id="hello-from-wellposed-ltd">Hello from Wellposed Ltd!</h2>
<p>Our New York based office conducts Computer Science R&amp;D and internal product development for fun and profit. We also selectively provide external consulting to help client businesses solve their algorithmic &amp; mathematical challenges and put the solutions into production.</p>
<p>If you'd like to learn more, shoot us an email <script type="text/javascript">
