<p>We believe that more theory is more power (in practice), and that within every interesting uniquely positioned business lies interesting unformalized research problems waiting to be solved, and that solving these problems creates nontrivial transformative value for those businesses.</p>
<p>For those who wish to sign up for the product announcements mailing list, please click <a href="http://eepurl.com/oALFL">here</a>.</p>
<p>Our current in progress product is a next generation set of high level, high perfomance (yes, both!) tools for numerical computation, data analysis, and mathematical modelling written in the fast, compiled, statically typed language Haskell.</p>
